1. *Nevjerojatno* je koliko on voli putovati. (It is incredible how much he loves to travel.)
2. Ona je učinila *nevjerojatno* uspješnu karijeru. (She made an incredibly successful career.)
3. On je imao *nevjerojatnu* hrabrost da se suoči s preprekama. (He had incredible courage to face the challenges.)
4. To je *nevjerojatno* kako je brzo on to isprogramirao. (It is amazing how quickly he programmed it.)
5. Ona je uspjela da napravi *nevjerojatne* stvari. (She managed to do incredible things.)